title: SHE Must Be Obeyed
overview: SHE Must Be Obeyed is a captivating series exposing the dark side of a successful Afrobeats music artist, SIYANBOLA ADEWALE (SHE), who would do anything to stay at the top. As SHE manipulates and exploits those around her, a determined group joins forces to expose her true nature, leading to a thrilling journey of deception and revenge in the music industry.
